tip.text: Good food. Kinda tasty but overall it's Ok. Me and my family including 1yo baby ate at the non-smoking area (I guess) but I can still smell the smoke that comes from upfront area. So be prepared.
The price is quite reasonable, good taste, walking distance from Jalan Banceuy. All of those including extra rice and free hot tea for around Rp.20,000,-
A new resort with a private hot spring pool for a couple or family with 2 optional choices to take. Either natural-like outdoor pool or modern in-room pool. There's also a playground and a sidewalk.
